original_title: Te Ribana 5 - The Story of Nei Tetaake
overview: Tetaake runs away from home after her stepfather threatens to sexually assault her. She travels around the country of Kiribati, pursued by her grandmother, and eventually takes refuge at the home of her friend Rianako and Rianoko's family. Tetaake tells her story to Rianoko and Rianoko's family shelters and protects Tetaake from her grandmother.
title: Te Ribana 5 - The Story of Nei Tetaake
